Does this happen every time you open the project?

It appears IntelliJ was trying to remove a balloon notification. Do you know what the balloon's message was?

That might help determine the cause of failure. It looks like a timing issue in the IntelliJ framework, but that's hard to know for sure with just this info.

The log file might help, if you can attach it. If you work with a Mac use this menu to find it: `Help > Show Log in Finder`. I don't know the equivalent on Windows, but I'm sure there is one.

Also, please attach the output of this menu: `Tools > Flutter > Flutter Doctor`.

Without additional information we're unfortunately not sure how to resolve this issue. We're going to close this bug for now, but please don't hesitate to comment on the bug if you have any more information for us; we're happy to reopen. Thanks for your contribution!
